00:47:35.970 --> 00:47:36.803
DANIEL MACIVOR: Why?

00:47:36.803 --> 00:47:38.400
CORI ELLISON: No, because--

00:47:38.400 --> 00:47:41.250
that's a truism
that you hear a lot.

00:47:41.250 --> 00:47:43.320
