00:47:50.280 --> 00:47:56.330
I think more that are
not actors in our cast.

00:47:56.330 --> 00:47:59.547
And I think it feels
like a more modern thing.

00:47:59.547 --> 00:48:00.380
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:48:00.380 --> 00:48:02.796
DANIEL MACIVOR: That there's
an attention to that in a way

00:48:02.796 --> 00:48:05.240
that there wasn't an
attention to it before.

00:48:05.240 --> 00:48:08.640
CORI ELLISON: Well, depends what
