00:48:08.640 --> 00:48:12.180
I mean, that's a very big,
sweeping generalization

00:48:12.180 --> 00:48:12.930
to make, I feel.

00:48:12.930 --> 00:48:14.513
DANIEL MACIVOR: My
feeling, as someone

00:48:14.513 --> 00:48:19.140
who doesn't know much
about opera, as I said--

00:48:19.140 --> 00:48:21.450
of the operas that I've
seen, my experience

00:48:21.450 --> 00:48:23.730
has been that acting
was not really--

00:48:23.730 --> 00:48:25.320
that didn't seem to
