00:48:28.754 --> 00:48:29.582
[LAUGHTER]

00:48:29.582 --> 00:48:31.040
DANIEL MACIVOR:
Yeah, so that was--

00:48:31.040 --> 00:48:32.429
and I think there's a lot of it.

00:48:32.429 --> 00:48:33.720
I think there is a lot of that.

00:48:33.720 --> 00:48:34.020
CORI ELLISON:
Well, I don't know.

00:48:34.020 --> 00:48:36.311
DANIEL MACIVOR: I think maybe
